{"tid":2167753,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"居英港人：移民最重要係決心。如果抱『如在英國生活不到，咪『留後路』回港』，這樣就不會成功。","createTime":"2020-08-21T10:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T10:04:43.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b7459c359849845005db481fca231c69b513677c","tid":2167753,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"問：你對於有意移民到英國的港人有何建議﹖<br />\n<br />\n答：他認為最重要是要有決心，「我在英國認識了很多來自香港的人，大家都有不同的故事、難處及驚險，但最後都決心留下來生活，展開另一個人生。這次香港人移民到英國的難度調低了，整件事情再簡單了，因此決心是最重要，要幾多錢是可解決的問題，<strong>千萬不要跟自己說：『如在英國生活不到，咪『留後路』回港』，這樣就不會成功。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2684739/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%91%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%88%E5%A4%A0%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%20%E7%A7%BB%E8%8B%B1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E6%8B%BF%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%BE%86%E5%81%9A%E7%94%9F%E6%84%8F%E6%88%96%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E3%80%82%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2684739%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E3%2580%2591%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%2585%2588%25E5%25A4%25A0%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB-%2520%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25EF%25BC%259A%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%258B%25BF%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%25BC%258F%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%2581%259A%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2584%258F%25E6%2588%2596%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E3%2580%2582%25E3%2580%258D&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=0a10703a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2684739/%E3%80%90%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%91%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B9%BE%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%88%E5%A4%A0%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%20%E7%A7%BB%E8%8B%B1%E6%B8%AF%E